{"tid":2444190,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"華納名下知名動畫 『飛天小女警The Powerpuff Girls』真人版公報主要演員！","createTime":"2021-03-12T14:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T15:38:02.000Z","uid":105567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"97a907a372078f2b6229494bcb32c345b4525c46","tid":2444190,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:18:43.000Z","msg":"●飛天小女警The Powerpuff Girls<br />\n華納名下 知名動畫品牌講述小鎮村的尤教授意外創造出三名飛天小女警 ：具領導能力的花花（Blossom）、最天直可愛的泡泡（Bubbles）與及 最具破壞力的毛毛（Buttercup）三人一邊上幼稚園一邊守護小鎮村與魔人啾啾（Mojo Jojo)等反派對抗。<br />\n動畫以可愛畫風與出格的形式(痛毆反派、 超展開的故事、 隱含女性主義兩性平權概念)而大受歡迎成為不小人的童年回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aKKkXfL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaKKkXfL.jpg&h=d7a41f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n●神盾局特工轉投CW<br />\n今次真人劇集找來 Chloe Bennet (Skye @Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.) Dove Cameron (迪士尼頻道 星光繼承者系列) 及 Yana Perrault (新進舞台音樂劇演員 )出演20多歲 脫離英雄行列的 花花、泡泡與毛毛。<br />\n<br />\n●20多年後的花花泡泡與毛毛<br />\n故事講述三人因為童年的行俠仗義經歷， 在成人生活中充滿創傷與憂鬱。甚至離群獨居互不往來意圖擺脫舊有框架， 可惜卻因為意外必須重新組隊，被迫面對『飛天小女警The Powerpuff Girls』這個久違的身份。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2CoBvAR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2CoBvAR.jpg&h=ee1e8cd3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6884bc8089e15eebdc2438e61215ebe52b5bbb4","tid":2444190,"uid":125168,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b671679274bad77ad0b05453934ce670d086fcbb","tid":2444190,"uid":362754,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:21:36.000Z","msg":"入到嚟諗緊會唔會有力架，點知真係有<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbc8afde954d381c1e58fc5ddecfad4a2350de0","tid":2444190,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T14:24:27.000Z","msg":"明明三隻公仔一樣色<br />\n係都要加個人黑人落去<br />\n同Ariel一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal